      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FINE SHINE (2) finished in the placings last time but could not have been more impressive before that in his convincing 24.63 win at Goulburn over 440m. Can measure up on top win two back. MASTER MCGRAW (4) comes here off a lightning win at Temora in 25.43 over 457m. Smart winner latest and looks a key chance on that form. GALBA MAJOR (1) was safely held last time out, finishing fifth at Temora over 457m behind MASTER MCGRAW (26.19) in a Grade 5. Was in the money the start prior. The form out of his last race has been franked. Will give the top chances plenty to think about. ZIPPING KAYLI (6) can improve on an unplaced run here last time out.",
